Application Users:

Single player
Start:
Player is loaded into a single player game room
During Game:
Player will have to guess Pokemon cry from the video games
Get 4 optional hints - each one deducts points
Longer the player takes to guess, will deduct points from possible points
End:
Final Score showcased
Multiplayer
Start:
Players are loaded into a multiplayer game room
During Game:
Players will have to guess Pokemon cry from video games
Get 4 hints optional hints - each one deduct points
Longer the player takes to guess, will deduct points from possible points
End:
Final standing of all players showcased
